in all-out attack on who God is,

00:35:38.419 --> 00:35:42.019
that we'd understand the opportunity that God has given us

00:35:42.019 --> 00:35:46.179
to declare Him to a lost and dying world.

00:35:47.139 --> 00:35:48.579
Because there are people that just flat out

00:35:49.219 --> 00:35:51.019
don't know who God is.

00:35:51.019 --> 00:35:54.659
They have their own little image of who they think God is.

00:35:55.899 --> 00:35:58.659
But we don't have to rely on some other source,

00:35:58.659 --> 00:36:01.659
we just go to His source.

00:36:02.939 --> 00:36:04.859
And this evening, as we would rejoice

00:36:04.859 --> 00:36:07.179
in what God has given us,

00:36:07.179 --> 00:36:10.219
I pray that God would help us to understand

00:36:10.219 --> 00:36:15.219
the responsibility to share that truth.

00:36:15.779 --> 00:36:18.539
Paul says, Him declare I unto thee.

00:36:18.539 --> 00:36:22.099
He says, how shall they hear without a preacher?

00:36:24.219 --> 00:36:25.299
We live in a society, we say,

00:36:25.299 --> 00:36:27.059
how can people think that way?

00:36:28.259 --> 00:36:30.339
You listen to the things that people say,

00:36:30.339 --> 00:36:32.499
and you say, how can they think that way?

00:36:32.499 --> 00:36:33.859
They don't know who God is.

00:36:34.899 --> 00:36:36.859
They don't know the truth of this book.

00:36:38.019 --> 00:36:39.059
Who's gonna tell them?

00:36:40.459 --> 00:36:44.299
Not the schoolteachers, right?

00:36:45.219 --> 00:36:48.259
Not Hollywood, not the politicians.

00:36:49.339 --> 00:36:51.339
No, not the media.

00:36:52.499 --> 00:36:53.939
Who's gonna tell them?

00:36:53.939 --> 00:36:56.779
Somebody that knows the truth, you and I.

00:36:56.779 --> 00:36:58.419
Stand up and give the truth.

00:36:58.419 --> 00:36:59.259
Let's pray.

00:36:59.259 --> 00:37:00.179
Father, we love you.

00:37:00.179 --> 00:37:01.819
Thank you for loving us.

00:37:01.819 --> 00:37:05.139
Thank you for revealing yourself to us through your word.

00:37:08.939 --> 00:37:12.579
We acknowledge this evening that we've been blessed.

00:37:14.579 --> 00:37:19.579
To know the truth of your word

00:37:20.659 --> 00:37:22.739
as you revealed yourself to us.

00:37:26.339 --> 00:37:31.339
I pray that as we, over the next couple of weeks,

00:37:31.859 --> 00:37:34.219
study the subject matter of theology,

00:37:34.219 --> 00:37:36.459
that our hearts would just rejoice.

00:37:37.939 --> 00:37:39.579
The very same time, I pray, God,

00:37:39.579 --> 00:37:43.739
that you'd help us to recognize the importance

00:37:44.579 --> 00:37:47.579
of proclaiming this truth to a lost and dying world.

00:37:48.739 --> 00:37:51.859
Understanding that there are so many in our society

00:37:54.419 --> 00:37:55.539
that do not know you.

00:38:00.579 --> 00:38:03.019
I pray, God, that you would help us.

00:38:03.019 --> 00:38:04.059
Bless our time of prayer.

00:38:04.059 --> 00:38:06.939
We thank you for the privilege of prayer.

00:38:06.939 --> 00:38:08.939
We pray that you would be honored and glorified

00:38:08.939 --> 00:38:10.099
through the remainder of our service.

00:38:10.099 --> 00:38:13.299
For it's in Christ's name we pray, amen.

00:38:13.299 --> 00:38:15.219
I did send out the prayer bulletin via email

00:38:15.219 --> 00:38:16.899
just before church this evening.

00:38:16.899 --> 00:38:18.979
And so those that are watching online.

